content: FiretpotFinance has launched its pre-sale phase of its $HOTT token, in BSCLAUNCH KDG among others and has managed to attract a good number of investors and strategic alliances that make it a great short-term project.It is at an early stage and they have been doing things very well encouraging participation and creating a great community.So keep up the good work congratulations to the team
